Name: EmployeeId
Description: Required; GUID; Auto-generated unique Employee identifier.

Name: EmployeeCode
Description: Required; Text; Unique employee code; Max length 10.

Name: FirstName
Description: Required; Text; Employee first name; Max length 100.

Name: LastName
Description: Required; Text; Last name; Max length 100.

Name: Gender
Description: Required; Lookup; Must reference Gender master.

Name: DateOfBirth
Description: Required; Date; Must be a valid birth date; Cannot be future. Age must be > 18

Name: Status
Description: Required; Lookup; Must reference Employment Status.

Name: GenderId
Description: Required; GUID; Auto-generated unique Gender identifier.

Name: GenderCode
Description: Required; Text; Gender code; Max length 10; Must be unique.

Name: EmployeeStatusId
Description: Required; GUID; Auto-generated unique Status identifier.

Name: Code
Description: Required; Text; Status code; Max length 10; Must be unique.

Name: Name
Description: Required; Text; Pay element name; Max length 100.

Name: IsTaxable
Description: Boolean; Indicates if element is taxable; Default = False.

Name: Name
Description: Required; Text; Pay element type name; Max length 100; Must be unique.

Name: Description
Description: Required; Text; Description of calculation type; Max length 100.

Name: Description
Description: Required; Text; Description of frequency; Max length 100.

Name: EmployeeId
Description: Required; GUID; References EmployeeId in Employee table.

Name: PayElementName
Description: Optional; Text; Pay element name; Derived.

Name: AttendanceId
Description: Required; GUID; Auto-generated unique attendance record ID.

Name: AttendanceDate
Description: Required; Date; Attendance date; Cannot be in future.

Name: CheckInTime
Description: Required; DateTime; Check-in timestamp; Must be before CheckOutTime.

Name: CheckOutTime
Description: Required; DateTime; Check-out timestamp; Must be after CheckInTime.

Name: SummaryId
Description: Required; GUID; Auto-generated summary record ID.

Name: DaysPresent
Description: Required; Number; Days present; 0 ≤ value ≤ TotalDays.

Name: DaysAbsent
Description: Required; Number; Days absent; 0 ≤ value ≤ TotalDays.

Name: NetPayableDays
Description: Required; Number; Net payable days = DaysPresent + LeaveDays − DaysAbsent.
